Dialogue: 10,0:01:43.65,0:01:45.13,Default,Ichiya,0,0,0,,N-Not working!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:05.90,0:02:07.94,Default,Ichiya,0,0,0,,I see you on TV all the time.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:08.90,0:02:10.61,Default,Ichiya,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:10.61,0:02:14.41,Default,Ichiya,0,0,0,,Though whenever I do, I can't help thinking \Nthat your acting is clumsy.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:16.14,0:02:19.79,Default,Ichiya,0,0,0,,It'd probably be considered great for a school arts festival.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:19.79,0:02:21.97,Default,Ichiya,0,0,0,,But you don’t have the attitude of a pro.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:22.41,0:02:25.12,Default,Mio,0,0,0,,H-Hey, hold on a minute!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:48.59,0:02:50.52,Default,Mio,0,0,0,,Who are you?!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:51.28,0:02:53.76,Default,Ichiya,0,0,0,,Kumagai Ichiya.\NNice to meet you.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:58.02,0:03:12.03,Song,,0,0,0,,Please don't let my heart go astray {https://utaten.com/lyric/to16064620/ - the text seems to be mostly bs tho}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:23.52,0:03:30.30,Song,,0,0,0,,I wanted to show it to you first—
Dialogue: 10,0:03:30.30,0:03:36.81,Song,,0,0,0,,the white skirt I bought yesterday
Dialogue: 10,0:03:36.81,0:03:43.58,Song,,0,0,0,,But you're so insensitive,
Dialogue: 10,0:03:44.56,0:03:49.07,Song,,0,0,0,,you didn't even notice
Dialogue: 10,0:03:49.07,0:03:54.31,Song,,0,0,0,,When I get into a bad mood,
Dialogue: 10,0:03:50.58,0:03:53.06,Song,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H500580&\i1\an1\fs20}Please stop the time {no clue}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:53.99,0:03:55.71,Song,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H500580&\i1\an1\fs20}Please change my mind
Dialogue: 10,0:03:55.71,0:04:01.20,Song,,0,0,0,,If you try to ask me why,
Dialogue: 10,0:03:57.42,0:04:00.01,Song,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H500580&\i1\an1\fs20}Please tell me why
Dialogue: 10,0:04:01.20,0:04:07.84,Song,,0,0,0,,The tears will fill my eyes
Dialogue: 10,0:04:07.84,0:04:13.84,Song,,0,0,0,,I understand, I'll turn my back on you
Dialogue: 10,0:04:13.84,0:04:21.35,Song,,0,0,0,,I’m running alone down a slope under the setting sun
Dialogue: 10,0:04:21.35,0:04:27.61,Song,,0,0,0,,Please chase after me
Dialogue: 10,0:04:27.61,0:04:35.74,Song,,0,0,0,,Don't let this love go astray
Dialogue: 10,0:04:52.25,0:04:53.39,Default,Aya,0,0,0,,Clumsy?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:53.39,0:04:57.12,Default,Mio,0,0,0,,Yes! He said it right to my face!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:57.12,0:05:00.53,Default,Mio,0,0,0,,Of course, I don’t see myself as a great actress.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:00.53,0:05:04.98,Default,Mio,0,0,0,,But it’s definitely not on the level \Nof an elementary school arts festival! {no idea why she brings up elementary school, it wasn't there originally, probably bc she's mad and misremembering it now; she's currently 15 btw}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:05.41,0:05:08.15,Default,Mio,0,0,0,,I didn't become a celebrity because I wanted to.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:08.15,0:05:09.62,Default,Aya,0,0,0,,Why, then?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:10.15,0:05:11.90,Default,Mio,0,0,0,,Why I did?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:12.50,0:05:13.79,Default,Mio,0,0,0,,Let me think...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:14.27,0:05:16.74,Default,Mio,0,0,0,,I've been on TV since I was little.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:16.74,0:05:19.28,Default,Mio,0,0,0,,And before I knew it, I became famous.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:19.28,0:05:22.04,Default,Mio,0,0,0,,I guess it just happened naturally.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:22.04,0:05:23.74,Default,Aya,0,0,0,,Happened naturally?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:24.47,0:05:28.35,Thought,Mio,0,0,0,,I'm Hagiwara Mio, aged 15,\NSagittarius, blood type O.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:28.35,0:05:32.02,Thought,Mio,0,0,0,,I'm a charming girl who's\Njust entered high school this spring.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:32.75,0:05:36.97,Thought,Mio,0,0,0,,I told Aya I got into showbiz naturally and without trying,
Dialogue: 10,0:05:37.47,0:05:40.29,Thought,Mio,0,0,0,,but in truth, I really enjoy being in this world.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:40.75,0:05:44.49,Thought,Mio,0,0,0,,If possible, I'd like to make acting \Nmy lifelong career.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:44.49,0:05:47.14,Thought,Mio,0,0,0,,That's what I have on my mind lately.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:50.00,0:05:51.36,Default,Mio,0,0,0,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:55.57,0:05:58.31,Thought,Mio,0,0,0,,Being an actress is really interesting.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:58.31,0:06:03.50,Thought,Mio,0,0,0,,You get to play so many roles, live so many lives, experience so many different things.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:03.50,0:06:07.08,Thought,Mio,0,0,0,,I can't think of another job like this!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:07.08,0:06:09.04,Thought,Ichiya,0,0,0,,You're clumsy.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:09.04,0:06:13.17,Thought,Mio,0,0,0,,Bleh! I remembered him again!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:25.28,0:06:30.98,Default,Glasses,0,0,0,,Your plan definitely appeals to me \Nin several ways.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:32.12,0:06:33.91,Default,Glasses,0,0,0,,The main one being...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:34.57,0:06:37.58,Default,Glasses,0,0,0,,That you, the director, \Nare a high school student.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:38.53,0:06:41.32,Default,Glasses,0,0,0,,Your demo tape is extremely well done.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:41.88,0:06:44.87,Default,Glasses,0,0,0,,I can feel the young talent \Nradiating from the screen.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:44.87,0:06:46.65,Default,Ichiya,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:47.16,0:06:49.93,Default,Glasses,0,0,0,,As for the actress you chose for the lead role…
Dialogue: 10,0:06:51.17,0:06:56.38,Default,Glasses,0,0,0,,Your choice showed sound judgment. \NShe has great potential.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:58.68,0:07:00.81,Default,Glasses,0,0,0,,Very well. We will sponsor you.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:01.27,0:07:02.93,Default,Osamu,0,0,0,,A-Are you serious?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:04.21,0:07:11.37,Default,Glasses,0,0,0,,In the current state of the film industry, \Nit’s difficult for Japanese films to become global hits.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:12.04,0:07:16.22,Default,Glasses,0,0,0,,But I dare say, I have high hopes \Nfor you young talents.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:16.22,0:07:18.17,Default,Glasses,0,0,0,,I just need you to remember one thing.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:19.90,0:07:22.92,Default,Glasses,0,0,0,,Our Somy Group is a commercial enterprise.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:22.92,0:07:26.63,Default,Glasses,0,0,0,,We don't fund your hobbies or charities.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:26.63,0:07:29.79,Default,Glasses,0,0,0,,You must create a certified hit film.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:39.55,0:07:47.07,Song,,0,0,0,,On a page of a magazine I bought at a train station,
Dialogue: 10,0:07:47.07,0:07:52.18,Song,,0,0,0,,I was looking at the horoscopes
Dialogue: 10,0:07:53.27,0:08:01.00,Song,,0,0,0,,It seems, one day I started caring
Dialogue: 10,0:08:01.00,0:08:04.82,Song,,0,0,0,,about your star sign
Dialogue: 10,0:08:07.83,0:08:14.67,Song,,0,0,0,,Even though I know we're just fooling around,
Dialogue: 10,0:08:14.67,0:08:21.76,Song,,0,0,0,,For some reason, I feel just a little embarrassed
Dialogue: 10,0:08:22.34,0:08:26.76,Song,,0,0,0,,You can see right through it—my poker face
Dialogue: 10,0:08:26.76,0:08:33.05,Song,,0,0,0,,As I pretend to be the same as always
Dialogue: 10,0:08:33.05,0:08:37.11,Song,,0,0,0,,But this time, I'm feeling lovely
Dialogue: 10,0:08:37.11,0:08:40.35,Song,,0,0,0,,My smile is a poker face
Dialogue: 10,0:08:40.35,0:08:52.79,Song,,0,0,0,,Please accept this palpitation \Nthat was born quietly over time...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:54.11,0:07:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Aya-san!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:28.58,0:08:31.99,Thought,Mio,0,0,0,,She really is a little different \Nfrom all the other idols.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:54.43,0:08:56.22,Default,Mio,0,0,0,,Aya, congratulations!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:56.22,0:08:57.79,Default,Mio,0,0,0,,That was really something!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:57.79,0:08:59.88,Default,Aya,0,0,0,,Thanks, Mio.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:03.04,0:09:10.56,Default,Mio,0,0,0,,Ah! I-It’s him! The guy who said I’m clumsy \Nand no better than an elementary school kid!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:10.56,0:09:12.10,Default,Ichiya,0,0,0,,Hey! We meet again.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:12.10,0:09:13.91,Default,Mio,0,0,0,,L-Look, you...!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:13.91,0:09:15.46,Default,Aya,0,0,0,,It's Kumagai Ichiya-kun.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:15.96,0:09:19.49,Default,Aya,0,0,0,,He spent two years in the US \Nstudying film production.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:19.49,0:09:21.50,Default,Aya,0,0,0,,He just came back this spring.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:21.50,0:09:23.60,Default,Mio,0,0,0,,Aya, you know this guy?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:26.25,0:09:29.70,Default,Aya,0,0,0,,He was my classmate in middle school \Nbefore my debut.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:30.22,0:09:31.16,Default,Mio,0,0,0,,Classmate?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:31.59,0:09:32.34,Default,Ichiya,0,0,0,,See ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:32.34,0:09:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:33.76,0:09:36.56,Default,Ichiya,0,0,0,,Keep practicing, \Nand you’ll become a worthy actress.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:52.81,0:09:55.78,Thought,Glasses,0,0,0,,Before you start filming,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:55.78,0:09:57.78,Thought,Glasses,0,0,0,,you'll need to get the word around.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:58.39,0:09:59.73,Thought,Ichiya,0,0,0,,Get the word around?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:59.73,0:10:00.84,Thought,Glasses,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:00.84,0:10:03.07,Thought,Glasses,0,0,0,,First, we need to build your profile.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:03.07,0:10:06.63,Thought,Glasses,0,0,0,,To that end, \Nyou'll shoot a promotional video.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:07.71,0:10:11.98,Thought,Glasses,0,0,0,,Put your gift into it \Nand we'll broadcast it on TV.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:11.98,0:10:16.58,Thought,Glasses,0,0,0,,We'll leave the novel imagery and the authors' names imprinted in people's minds.\N
Dialogue: 10,0:10:16.58,0:10:20.06,Thought,Glasses,0,0,0,,Then we'll announce \Nthe production of the film.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:20.60,0:10:24.02,Thought,Glasses,0,0,0,,I'm putting my trust in you guys, \Nso please make it good.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:24.60,0:10:29.80,Thought,Glasses,0,0,0,,After all, it will feature Sawaki Aya, Somy Records' top idol and pride.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:39.73,0:10:41.83,Thought,Aya,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you, Ichiya-kun.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:03.77,0:11:07.02,Song,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H500580&\i1\an1\fs20}Don't ask me why... {no clue}
Dialogue: 10,0:11:11.63,0:11:13.55,Song,,0,0,0,,While you're waiting for a bus,
Dialogue: 10,0:11:15.20,0:11:19.03,Song,,0,0,0,,I'm sitting on your suitcase
Dialogue: 10,0:11:19.03,0:11:26.52,Song,,0,0,0,,and watching the endless sea
Dialogue: 10,0:11:26.52,0:11:28.67,Song,,0,0,0,,A white ship
Dialogue: 10,0:11:30.17,0:11:33.86,Song,,0,0,0,,gently sails away,
Dialogue: 10,0:11:33.86,0:11:39.70,Song,,0,0,0,,Taking away our golden summer
Dialogue: 10,0:11:41.79,0:11:47.19,Song,,0,0,0,,Again as my childhood friend,
Dialogue: 10,0:11:49.17,0:11:53.94,Song,,0,0,0,,You return to the big city
Dialogue: 10,0:11:57.47,0:12:04.90,Song,,0,0,0,,I hold unspoken words in my right hand
Dialogue: 10,0:12:04.90,0:12:11.15,Song,,0,0,0,,While waving lightly with my left hand
Dialogue: 10,0:12:12.29,0:12:19.20,Song,,0,0,0,,I'll keep your smiles in my heart
Dialogue: 10,0:12:19.20,0:12:25.68,Song,,0,0,0,,Hey, please shine on for me
Dialogue: 10,0:12:32.05,0:12:34.22,Default,Mio,0,0,0,,You've got another big hit?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:34.22,0:12:34.78,Default,Aya,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:34.78,0:12:37.03,Default,Aya,0,0,0,,Maybe it's thanks to that promotional video?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:37.03,0:12:38.57,Default,Mio,0,0,0,,It was nicely done.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:38.57,0:12:40.39,Default,Mio,0,0,0,,It shows off all your good points.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:40.39,0:12:42.06,Default,Aya,0,0,0,,Oh, that? Ichiya-kun filmed it.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:42.06,0:12:44.41,Default,Mio,0,0,0,,Ichiya? {\i1}That{\i0} Ichiya...?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:44.41,0:12:45.42,Default,Osamu,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:45.42,0:12:49.33,Song,,0,0,0,,I want your love that fills with sensation {"I want your love" from the official OST CD}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:46.20,0:12:47.04,Default,Aya,0,0,0,,Ichiya-kun!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:47.79,0:12:49.98,Default,Osamu,0,0,0,,Wanna celebrate with us?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:49.33,0:12:53.00,Song,,0,0,0,,Give you all my body tonight
Dialogue: 10,0:12:49.98,0:12:51.44,Default,Aya,0,0,0,,Celebrate?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:51.44,0:12:56.91,Default,Osamu,0,0,0,,We're throwing a small party to celebrate \Nthe success of your promotional video.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:53.00,0:12:56.92,Song,,0,0,0,,I need your love that follows your emotions
Dialogue: 10,0:12:56.91,0:12:59.05,Default,Aya,0,0,0,,Wow! Thanks!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:56.92,0:13:00.99,Song,,0,0,0,,Every time it seems so without you
Dialogue: 10,0:13:05.70,0:13:08.59,Default,Yasushi,0,0,0,,If we're going the same way,\Nwe can share the ride.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:08.59,0:13:10.19,Default,Ichiya,0,0,0,,Where do you live?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:10.19,0:13:11.14,Default,Mio,0,0,0,,Seijo.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:11.14,0:13:12.73,Default,Ichiya,0,0,0,,It's on the way, then. Get in.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:13.54,0:13:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Okay...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:27.83,0:13:30.00,Default,Ichiya,0,0,0,,Your face is expressive enough.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:31.27,0:13:35.00,Default,Ichiya,0,0,0,,The timings aren't bad either. \NYou have a good sense for acting.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:35.46,0:13:37.30,Default,Ichiya,0,0,0,,But the delivery is unconvincing. {/the way you say the lines}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:38.40,0:13:42.80,Default,Ichiya,0,0,0,,It will take some effort, but with a bit more practice, \Nyou'll improve as an actress.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:43.30,0:13:46.05,Default,Ichiya,0,0,0,,When I said you're clumsy, \NI didn't mean any harm.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:53.43,0:13:56.11,Default,Mio,0,0,0,,"But the delivery isn't quite there.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:56.11,0:13:59.22,Default,Mio,0,0,0,,With a bit more practice, \Nyou'll improve as an actress."
Dialogue: 10,0:13:59.75,0:14:01.64,Default,Mio,0,0,0,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:02.24,0:14:05.56,Default,Mio,0,0,0,,He's far too late to try \Nand make amends with me.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:06.37,0:14:09.14,Thought,Ichiya,0,0,0,,When I said you're clumsy, \NI didn't mean any harm.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:14.50,0:14:18.32,Default,Mio,0,0,0,,Maybe he's not such a bad guy after all.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:28.83,0:14:31.33,Default,Mio,0,0,0,,Coming!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:31.33,0:14:34.04,Default,Mio's Manager,0,0,0,,Come on! Are you still sleeping?\NTurn on the TV!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:34.04,0:14:35.40,Default,Mio,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:35.40,0:14:38.04,Default,Mio's Manager,0,0,0,,Make sure you don't drop your jaw \Nwhen you see it, Mio.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:38.04,0:14:41.04,Default,Mio's Manager,0,0,0,,You've been cast \Nin the lead role in a feature film!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:41.70,0:14:44.45,Default,Mio's Manager,0,0,0,,President already signed the contract!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:47.57,0:14:50.56,Thought,Mio's Manager,0,0,0,,Mio, this is your chance to make it big!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:50.56,0:14:54.12,Thought,Mio's Manager,0,0,0,,At last, a star will be born \Nunder our production!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:03.56,0:15:06.17,Default,Yasushi,0,0,0,,Oh, it's you, Mio-chan? \NI'm glad you came.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:06.17,0:15:07.80,Default,Yasushi,0,0,0,,Come on in, hurry up.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:07.80,0:15:08.70,Default,Mio,0,0,0,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:11.08,0:15:16.21,Default,Mio,0,0,0,,My manager suddenly called me this morning, \Nbut I didn't quite understand everything...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:16.21,0:15:18.63,Default,Osamu,0,0,0,,It's pretty straightforward.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:18.63,0:15:21.15,Default,Osamu,0,0,0,,We just want you to be the star of our movie.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:21.15,0:15:22.47,Default,Mio,0,0,0,,B-But...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:22.47,0:15:24.81,Default,Ichiya,0,0,0,,Sorry we didn't consult you beforehand.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:24.81,0:15:30.27,Default,Yasushi,0,0,0,,But Okita-san suggested that announcing \Nthe production this way would be more impactful.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:30.27,0:15:34.20,Default,Osamu,0,0,0,,Okita-san is one of Somy's head managers \Nthat is backing us.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:35.43,0:15:37.22,Default,Osamu,0,0,0,,I'll introduce our staff.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:37.22,0:15:38.65,Default,Osamu,0,0,0,,Otomo Yasushi,
Dialogue: 10,0:15:38.65,0:15:40.84,Default,Osamu,0,0,0,,he's the producer for this one.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:40.84,0:15:41.67,Default,Yasushi,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:42.11,0:15:44.09,Default,Osamu,0,0,0,,I'm Kani Osamu, the cameraman.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:44.09,0:15:46.09,Default,Osamu,0,0,0,,Mio-chan, I'll film you beautifully.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:46.09,0:15:48.70,Default,Osamu,0,0,0,,And this is Hosaka Minoru, art director.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:48.70,0:15:49.66,Default,Minoru,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:50.09,0:15:52.31,Default,Osamu,0,0,0,,Lighting—Oda Shuji.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:52.31,0:15:53.72,Default,Shuji,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:53.72,0:15:56.02,Default,Osamu,0,0,0,,Recording, Fujii Daisuke.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:56.02,0:15:56.81,Default,Daisuke,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:56.81,0:16:00.27,Default,Osamu,0,0,0,,Finally, scriptwriter and director—\NKumagai Ichiya.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:00.27,0:16:01.16,Default,Ichiya,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:01.16,0:16:02.65,Default,Mio,0,0,0,,Ah... Excuse me...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:08.57,0:16:09.81,Default,Mio,0,0,0,,N-Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:09.81,0:16:13.16,Default,Osamu,0,0,0,,Hooray! Mio-chan agreed to work with us!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:13.16,0:16:14.37,Default,Minoru,0,0,0,,We've got it!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:14.37,0:16:17.11,Default,Minoru,0,0,0,,That means you need \Nto speed up the script, Ichiya.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:17.11,0:16:19.98,Default,Ichiya,0,0,0,,Yeah! I'm on it—almost finished.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:20.42,0:16:22.88,Default,Ichiya,0,0,0,,I guess we'll start filming \Nduring summer vacation.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:22.88,0:16:24.78,Default,Daisuke,0,0,0,,We can't forget about the school.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:24.78,0:16:26.46,Default,Osamu,0,0,0,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:26.46,0:16:30.12,Default,Osamu,0,0,0,,When making a movie, \Nwe can't let school distract us.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:30.12,0:16:33.29,Default,Yasushi,0,0,0,,Calm down, Osamu. \NNo need to be so extreme.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:36.47,0:16:39.56,Thought,Mio,0,0,0,,Their enthusiasm energized me as well.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:39.56,0:16:43.31,Thought,Mio,0,0,0,,They... love cinema with all their hearts.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:44.01,0:16:46.30,Thought,Mio,0,0,0,,It's so nice to love what you're doing.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:49.40,0:16:50.47,Default,Ichiya,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:51.61,0:16:55.91,Default,Ichiya,0,0,0,,Everyone was thrilled when you \Nagreed to work with us.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:55.91,0:16:56.83,Default,Mio,0,0,0,,Everyone?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:56.83,0:16:59.08,Default,Ichiya,0,0,0,,Well, of course, I'm happy about it too.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:02.63,0:17:04.54,Default,Ichiya,0,0,0,,Do you want to go see a movie?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:04.54,0:17:05.88,Default,Mio,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:17:05.88,0:17:07.59,Default,Mio,0,0,0,,Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:19.93,0:17:25.82,Default,Ichiya,0,0,0,,They call actresses such as Lauren Bacall \Nand Marlene Dietrich "handsome women".
Dialogue: 10,0:17:37.67,0:17:40.24,Default,Mio,0,0,0,,"Handsome" is usually reserved for males.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:40.24,0:17:42.81,Default,Ichiya,0,0,0,,Lately, it's been used for ladies too.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:42.81,0:17:47.03,Default,Ichiya,0,0,0,,It means you're cool, intelligent and determined... \NOr something to that effect.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:47.55,0:17:50.31,Default,Ichiya,0,0,0,,It's like an ultimate compliment.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:51.32,0:17:56.20,Default,Ichiya,0,0,0,,Making a captivating movie \Nwith an overwhelmingly handsome heroine
Dialogue: 10,0:17:56.20,0:17:59.97,Default,Ichiya,0,0,0,,alongside my friends and peers... \Nthat's my dream.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:02.35,0:18:05.94,Default,Ichiya,0,0,0,,When I first saw you on TV, \NI felt you were {\i1}that{\i0} heroine.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:09.07,0:18:10.90,Default,Ichiya,0,0,0,,We'll capture your beauty!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:12.90,0:18:14.61,Default,Ichiya,0,0,0,,You can trust us with it.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:22.78,0:18:26.48,Thought,Mio,0,0,0,,I've never seen him like that...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:28.54,0:18:31.33,Thought,Mio,0,0,0,,Every time we meet, \NI discover a new side of him.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:32.00,0:18:34.84,Thought,Mio,0,0,0,,He's confident... And stern.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:34.84,0:18:37.39,Thought,Mio,0,0,0,,Yet he's shy and gentle.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:38.51,0:18:41.56,Thought,Mio,0,0,0,,I want to get to know Ichiya better.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:47.65,0:18:50.15,Default,Glasses,0,0,0,,It's a good script. Let's roll with it.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:50.15,0:18:52.28,Default,Glasses,0,0,0,,Can you start filming immediately?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:52.28,0:18:53.05,Default,Ichiya,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:06.46,0:19:07.54,Default,Ichiya,0,0,0,,Cut!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:55.01,0:19:59.49,Thought,Mio,0,0,0,,Ichiya, you're devoting yourself \Nfully to this movie.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:59.49,0:20:02.01,Thought,Mio,0,0,0,,Completely oblivious to the outside world.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:02.01,0:20:04.39,Thought,Mio,0,0,0,,I like that about you.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:04.39,0:20:06.92,Thought,Mio,0,0,0,,But I wish you looked at me more...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:06.92,0:20:08.21,Default,Ichiya,0,0,0,,Ready?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:08.82,0:20:09.80,Default,Ichiya,0,0,0,,Start!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:43.76,0:20:44.79,Default,Aya,0,0,0,,Mio!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:48.31,0:20:50.17,Default,Aya,0,0,0,,Is the shoot going smoothly?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:50.17,0:20:54.70,Default,Mio,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's going great. \NI feel like we're about to wrap it up.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:54.70,0:20:57.69,Default,Aya,0,0,0,,Mio, you've become so much more lively \Nsince you started.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:57.69,0:20:59.38,Default,Mio,0,0,0,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:59.82,0:21:01.11,Default,Mio,0,0,0,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:01.11,0:21:03.30,Default,Mio,0,0,0,,You don't look like your usual self.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:03.30,0:21:04.16,Default,Mio,0,0,0,,Aya...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:06.41,0:21:09.91,Default,Aya,0,0,0,,This love is already over,\Nso I thought I'd forget about it.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:09.91,0:21:10.92,Default,Aya,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:12.96,0:21:16.13,Default,Aya,0,0,0,,Ichiya-kun and I were dating\Nin the middle school. {first year}
Dialogue: 10,0:21:20.03,0:21:23.00,Default,Aya,0,0,0,,My first kiss was with him too.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:35.86,0:21:39.49,Default,Aya,0,0,0,,I made the first step \Nand confessed my love to him.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:42.49,0:21:45.28,Default,Aya,0,0,0,,After that, we walked home together every day.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:45.89,0:21:48.77,Default,Aya,0,0,0,,We went on dates several times a month.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:49.86,0:21:51.56,Default,Aya,0,0,0,,And in the autumn...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:52.24,0:21:53.85,Default,Aya,0,0,0,,We kissed.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:57.48,0:21:59.30,Default,Mio,0,0,0,,Why did you break up?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:59.67,0:22:00.97,Thought,Aya,0,0,0,,Study abroad?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:00.97,0:22:04.30,Thought,Ichiya,0,0,0,,Yes. For two years, maybe more.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:05.09,0:22:07.26,Thought,Ichiya,0,0,0,,I'll be studying film-making in the US.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:07.26,0:22:11.81,Thought,Aya,0,0,0,,I see. I also got my debut arranged \Nthrough my singing teacher. {maybe "Utano-sensei"}
Dialogue: 10,0:22:11.81,0:22:13.81,Thought,Ichiya,0,0,0,,I see. Congratulations.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:14.31,0:22:17.77,Thought,Aya,0,0,0,,I guess this is goodbye, then?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:18.48,0:22:20.38,Thought,Ichiya,0,0,0,,Yes. So it seems.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:21.12,0:22:22.32,Thought,Mio,0,0,0,,So long.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:22.32,0:22:24.53,Thought,Ichiya,0,0,0,,Yes... Bye-bye.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:30.78,0:22:33.70,Default,Aya,0,0,0,,I wanted him to tell me to wait three years.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:33.70,0:22:38.20,Default,Aya,0,0,0,,But Ichiya left without a word.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:39.21,0:22:40.67,Default,Mio,0,0,0,,I had no idea.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:41.51,0:22:43.63,Default,Aya,0,0,0,,I envy you now.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:43.63,0:22:46.16,Default,Aya,0,0,0,,You spend all your time with Ichiya.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:46.62,0:22:47.70,Default,Mio,0,0,0,,Aya...
Dialogue: 10,0:23:06.53,0:23:10.32,Thought,Mio,0,0,0,,This love is already over,\Nso I thought I'd forget about it.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:10.32,0:23:12.52,Thought,Mio,0,0,0,,But... But...
Dialogue: 10,0:23:17.04,0:23:20.42,Default,Osamu,0,0,0,,Why won't you acknowledge\NMio-chan's feelings for you? {no clue what's sashitare}
Dialogue: 10,0:23:21.92,0:23:24.92,Default,Osamu,0,0,0,,It's obvious if you look at it from the outside.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:24.92,0:23:30.47,Default,Osamu,0,0,0,,Whenever Mio-chan sees you, the love in her eyes burns so intensely that it's impossible to ignore!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:30.47,0:23:32.42,Default,Ichiya,0,0,0,,I love her too.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:32.85,0:23:37.52,Default,Osamu,0,0,0,,Then why don't you ever say \Na single kind word to her?
Dialogue: 10,0:23:37.52,0:23:43.90,Default,Ichiya,0,0,0,,Osamu, make no mistake: when I said I love her, \NI meant the actress, Hagiwara Mio.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:44.32,0:23:48.38,Default,Osamu,0,0,0,,When you say "the actress"... \Nyou mean her as a movie asset? {/material}
Dialogue: 10,0:23:48.38,0:23:49.82,Default,Osamu,0,0,0,,Or as a girl?
Dialogue: 10,0:23:51.28,0:23:52.59,Default,Ichiya,0,0,0,,Neither.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:52.59,0:23:54.95,Default,Osamu,0,0,0,,So you're {\i1}not{\i0} interested in her, after all?
Dialogue: 10,0:23:54.95,0:23:58.58,Default,Ichiya,0,0,0,,The way I see Hagiwara is nothing like that
Dialogue: 10,0:24:03.42,0:24:04.55,Default,Osamu,0,0,0,,Mio-chan.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:07.30,0:24:10.30,Default,Osamu,0,0,0,,Ichiya! Mio-chan just overheard you.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:28.20,0:24:33.16,Thought,Mio,0,0,0,,I'm just an asset... \NMerely a tool for Ichiya to make a movie with.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:36.54,0:24:37.62,Thought,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:37.62,0:24:39.00,Thought,,0,0,0,,It can't be...!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:55.08,0:24:56.39,Default,Ichiya,0,0,0,,Cut!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:56.39,0:25:00.55,Default,Ichiya,0,0,0,,Hagiwara! You call that acting? \NI can't feel any emotion in it!
Dialogue: 10,0:25:00.96,0:25:02.56,Default,Mio,0,0,0,,S-Sorry!
Dialogue: 10,0:25:03.69,0:25:06.31,Default,Ichiya,0,0,0,,No, that won't do! \NOne more take!
Dialogue: 10,0:25:06.31,0:25:07.23,Default,Mio,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 10,0:25:10.53,0:25:13.89,Thought,Mio,0,0,0,,I'm just a tool for making movies.
Dialogue: 10,0:25:13.89,0:25:17.87,Default,Ichiya,0,0,0,,Good... Looking great, Osamu. \NZoom out! {no clue}
Dialogue: 10,0:25:18.98,0:25:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Ichiya's recent scripts are amazing.
Dialogue: 10,0:25:21.32,0:25:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, incredibly thrilling. {unsure}
Dialogue: 10,0:25:23.58,0:25:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Mio-chan's doing great too.
Dialogue: 10,0:25:25.09,0:25:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,She's totally believable! {no clue, newoagenai? mewoagenai? neither makes sense here}
Dialogue: 10,0:25:40.10,0:25:41.93,Default,Yasushi,0,0,0,,Wh-What did you say?
Dialogue: 10,0:25:42.83,0:25:45.17,Default,Yasushi,0,0,0,,The production was halted?
Dialogue: 10,0:25:45.17,0:25:47.32,Default,Glasses,0,0,0,,The order was given from above.
Dialogue: 10,0:25:47.32,0:25:51.15,Default,Yasushi,0,0,0,,Okita-san, I thought you were the department head. \NWho could be above you?
Dialogue: 10,0:25:51.74,0:25:53.12,Default,Glasses,0,0,0,,The president.
Dialogue: 10,0:25:53.70,0:25:55.89,Default,Glasses,0,0,0,,My own father.
Dialogue: 10,0:25:55.89,0:25:57.87,Default,Yasushi,0,0,0,,O-Oh no...
Dialogue: 10,0:25:57.87,0:26:02.40,Default,Glasses,0,0,0,,"Film-making is a waste of time; \Nready-made software is a better investment."
Dialogue: 10,0:26:02.96,0:26:07.65,Default,Glasses,0,0,0,,That's his judgment as an entrepreneur.
Dialogue: 10,0:26:11.12,0:26:16.43,Default,Osamu,0,0,0,,How could they do that? We've only got one scene left to film—the story's climax!
Dialogue: 10,0:26:16.43,0:26:20.52,Default,Yasushi,0,0,0,,If we want to keep filming, \Nwe'll need to secure additional funding.
Dialogue: 10,0:26:20.52,0:26:22.52,Default,Osamu,0,0,0,,Are you saying we have to give up?!
Dialogue: 10,0:26:22.52,0:26:24.31,Default,Yasushi,0,0,0,,There's no other choice.
Dialogue: 10,0:26:25.69,0:26:32.40,Thought,Ichiya,0,0,0,,For the sake of this movie, I've already set aside \Neverything I had—school, family, and...
Dialogue: 10,0:26:36.63,0:26:38.95,Thought,Ichiya,0,0,0,,I won't let them stop us now.
Dialogue: 10,0:26:38.95,0:26:40.18,Thought,Ichiya,0,0,0,,Absolutely not!
Dialogue: 10,0:26:41.41,0:26:42.50,Default,Ichiya,0,0,0,,We'll finish filming!
Dialogue: 10,0:26:43.04,0:26:43.75,Default,MULTIPLE,0,0,0,,Ichiya!
Dialogue: 10,0:26:50.92,0:26:53.47,Default,Mio,0,0,0,,Um... Excuse me...
Dialogue: 10,0:26:53.47,0:26:56.30,Default,Ichiya,0,0,0,,Don't worry. We'll finish it.
Dialogue: 10,0:26:56.30,0:26:57.43,Default,Mio,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 10,0:26:57.43,0:27:00.51,Default,Ichiya,0,0,0,,I borrowed money from the bank \Nusing my apartment as collateral.
Dialogue: 10,0:27:00.51,0:27:02.60,Default,Ichiya,0,0,0,,Everyone worked hard \Nto make it happen. {these last six months}
Dialogue: 10,0:27:02.60,0:27:04.60,Default,Ichiya,0,0,0,,We can't give up now.
Dialogue: 10,0:27:10.61,0:27:13.63,Default,Ichiya,0,0,0,,All that's left is a car chase scene, don't worry.
Dialogue: 10,0:27:14.26,0:27:15.15,Default,Ichiya,0,0,0,,See ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:27:44.87,0:27:47.92,Default,Yasushi,0,0,0,,Ichiya, are you sure you can manage?
Dialogue: 10,0:27:48.40,0:27:51.80,Default,Ichiya,0,0,0,,You'll see. \NI'll nail this scene.
Dialogue: 10,0:27:57.95,0:28:01.39,Default,Mio,0,0,0,,Osamu-kun told me \Nthat you're handling the stunt work.
Dialogue: 10,0:28:02.22,0:28:06.00,Default,Ichiya,0,0,0,,You came to see my stunt? \NWhat a curious audience I've got.
Dialogue: 10,0:28:06.00,0:28:06.83,Default,Mio,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 10,0:28:08.42,0:28:11.25,Default,Mio,0,0,0,,I'm... worried.
Dialogue: 10,0:28:11.90,0:28:13.24,Default,Ichiya,0,0,0,,Why's that?
Dialogue: 10,0:28:18.13,0:28:19.18,Default,Ichiya,0,0,0,,Mio...
Dialogue: 10,0:28:23.14,0:28:25.93,Default,Mio,0,0,0,,Good luck. Don't get hurt.
Dialogue: 10,0:28:25.93,0:28:26.77,Default,Mio,0,0,0,,Bye.
Dialogue: 10,0:28:32.57,0:28:34.65,Default,Osamu,0,0,0,,Do you read me, Ichiya?
Dialogue: 10,0:28:34.65,0:28:35.88,Default,Osamu,0,0,0,,Are you ready?
Dialogue: 10,0:28:38.86,0:28:41.10,Default,Ichiya,0,0,0,,Yeah. Good to go.
Dialogue: 10,0:28:54.90,0:28:56.45,Default,Ichiya,0,0,0,,Start the camera!
Dialogue: 10,0:29:34.04,0:29:35.88,Thought,Ichiya,0,0,0,,Timing is crucial now!
Dialogue: 10,0:29:43.43,0:29:44.51,Thought,Ichiya,0,0,0,,Did it!
Dialogue: 10,0:29:51.59,0:29:52.71,Default,Osamu,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 10,0:29:52.71,0:29:54.67,Default,Yasushi,0,0,0,,We did it!
Dialogue: 10,0:29:58.72,0:30:00.18,Thought,Ichiya,0,0,0,,Now the bend.
Dialogue: 10,0:30:02.53,0:30:03.74,Default,Ichiya,0,0,0,,N-Not working!
Dialogue: 10,0:30:03.74,0:30:06.20,Default,Osamu,0,0,0,,What are you doing, Ichiya?\NSlow down!
Dialogue: 10,0:30:10.50,0:30:12.62,Default,Ichiya,0,0,0,,That last stunt busted the bike.
Dialogue: 10,0:30:12.62,0:30:14.63,Default,Ichiya,0,0,0,,This just got real!
Dialogue: 10,0:30:26.22,0:30:27.41,Default,Mio,0,0,0,,Ichiya!
Dialogue: 10,0:30:31.38,0:30:32.84,Default,Yasushi,0,0,0,,Ichiya!
Dialogue: 10,0:30:37.01,0:30:38.26,Default,Osamu,0,0,0,,Ichiya!
Dialogue: 10,0:30:46.57,0:30:48.36,Default,Osamu,0,0,0,,Ichiya, answer me!
Dialogue: 10,0:30:48.36,0:30:49.14,Default,Osamu,0,0,0,,Ichiya!
Dialogue: 10,0:31:06.89,0:31:09.71,Default,Yasushi,0,0,0,,Mio-chan, hang on! Mio-chan!
Dialogue: 10,0:31:10.72,0:31:11.89,Thought,Mio,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 10,0:31:12.98,0:31:15.16,Thought,Mio,0,0,0,,Why did this have to happen?!
Dialogue: 10,0:31:21.23,0:31:24.40,Default,Osamu,0,0,0,,I don't believe this... \NAnswer me, please!
Dialogue: 10,0:31:24.40,0:31:25.73,Default,Osamu,0,0,0,,Ichiya!
Dialogue: 10,0:31:27.45,0:31:28.53,Default,Ichiya,0,0,0,,Osamu?
Dialogue: 10,0:31:29.03,0:31:30.60,Default,Osamu,0,0,0,,Ichiya? Is that you, Ichiya!
Dialogue: 10,0:31:30.60,0:31:32.94,Default,Minoru,0,0,0,,Ichiya! You're alive?!
Dialogue: 10,0:31:34.11,0:31:37.04,Default,Ichiya,0,0,0,,Yeah... Made it out, barely.
Dialogue: 10,0:31:37.04,0:31:41.44,Default,Ichiya,0,0,0,,The bike's burning right next to me,\Nwhat a thrilling sight!
Dialogue: 10,0:32:05.86,0:32:07.01,Default,Ichiya,0,0,0,,Silly...
Dialogue: 10,0:32:07.61,0:32:08.99,Default,Ichiya,0,0,0,,You're crying again.
Dialogue: 10,0:32:12.44,0:32:15.83,Default,MULTIPLE,0,0,0,,Ichiya! Hang on, Ichiya!
Dialogue: 10,0:32:14.83,0:32:15.83,Overlap,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 10,0:32:17.96,0:32:23.42,Default,Ichiya,0,0,0,,From the moment you're flung into the air until you hit the ground, time seems to slow down, strangely.
Dialogue: 10,0:32:23.42,0:32:26.26,Default,Ichiya,0,0,0,,It was just like slow motion.
Dialogue: 10,0:32:26.26,0:32:30.93,Default,Ichiya,0,0,0,,Then a thought flashed through my mind: \N"Ah... so this is how I die."
Dialogue: 10,0:32:30.93,0:32:33.33,Default,Ichiya,0,0,0,,It reminded me of all those past regrets.
Dialogue: 10,0:32:33.89,0:32:39.46,Default,Ichiya,0,0,0,,Like turning my back on my true feelings, \Nor not letting myself respond to her.
Dialogue: 10,0:32:40.48,0:32:43.98,Default,Ichiya,0,0,0,,I wanted to make a good movie \Nwithout making any compromises.
Dialogue: 10,0:32:43.98,0:32:47.85,Default,Ichiya,0,0,0,,That's why I put everything\Nnot related to the movie aside.
Dialogue: 10,0:32:47.85,0:32:52.31,Default,Osamu,0,0,0,,What's the point telling me that, \Nya blockhead?
Dialogue: 10,0:33:01.08,0:33:04.88,Default,Osamu,0,0,0,,If you don't retell this to Mio-chan, \NI'll make you regret it.
Dialogue: 10,0:33:04.88,0:33:06.09,Default,Mio,0,0,0,,Good afternoon!
Dialogue: 10,0:33:06.09,0:33:08.30,Default,Osamu,0,0,0,,Wow, perfect timing!
Dialogue: 10,0:33:08.30,0:33:11.23,Default,Osamu,0,0,0,,Can you believe we were just gossiping about you, Mio-chan?
Dialogue: 10,0:33:11.23,0:33:12.01,Default,Mio,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 10,0:33:12.01,0:33:14.87,Default,Osamu,0,0,0,,Well, I'm sure Ichiya will be happy to fill you in.
Dialogue: 10,0:33:14.87,0:33:16.35,Default,Mio,0,0,0,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 10,0:33:16.35,0:33:17.35,Default,Ichiya,0,0,0,,Osamu!
Dialogue: 10,0:33:17.85,0:33:19.83,Default,Osamu,0,0,0,,Don't hold anything back, Ichiya.
Dialogue: 10,0:33:27.57,0:33:28.97,Default,Mio,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 10,0:33:29.53,0:33:31.39,Default,Ichiya,0,0,0,,Ah? Nothing.
Dialogue: 10,0:33:39.37,0:33:40.96,Default,Mio,0,0,0,,Does it still hurt?
Dialogue: 10,0:33:41.37,0:33:43.28,Default,Ichiya,0,0,0,,No, I'm fine now.
Dialogue: 10,0:33:43.92,0:33:44.90,Default,Ichiya,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 10,0:33:45.59,0:33:46.96,Default,Mio,0,0,0,,No! Don't get up!
Dialogue: 10,0:33:48.21,0:33:50.24,Default,Mio,0,0,0,,You need to stay in bed.
Dialogue: 10,0:34:03.34,0:34:07.57,Default,Ichiya,0,0,0,,I love you, and I always have.
Dialogue: 10,0:34:08.69,0:34:10.30,Default,Ichiya,0,0,0,,Don't cry anymore. {/I'll never again make you cry.}
Dialogue: 10,0:34:11.78,0:34:13.01,Default,Mio,0,0,0,,Ichiya...
Dialogue: 10,0:34:23.69,0:34:26.84,Default,Mio,0,0,0,,So, Ichiya, what happened to our movie?
Dialogue: 10,0:34:26.84,0:34:31.45,Default,Ichiya,0,0,0,,Well, there's still some work to do. \NProbably only after I recover.
Dialogue: 10,0:34:31.45,0:34:33.09,Default,Mio,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:34:33.09,0:34:33.93,Default,Mio,0,0,0,,Tell me.
Dialogue: 10,0:34:35.45,0:34:39.71,Default,Mio,0,0,0,,Will you use me again \Nwhen you make your next movie? {/second movie}
Dialogue: 10,0:34:39.71,0:34:41.27,Default,Ichiya,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 10,0:34:41.92,0:34:44.35,Default,Ichiya,0,0,0,,Like I can let someone else have you!
Dialogue: 10,0:34:44.35,0:34:48.27,Default,Ichiya,0,0,0,,Hagiwara Mio will always be\Nmy exclusive heroine.
Dialogue: 10,0:35:06.63,0:35:19.76,Song,,0,0,0,,Please don't let my heart go astray
Dialogue: 10,0:35:31.78,0:35:38.87,Song,,0,0,0,,I want to be reflected more beautifully
Dialogue: 10,0:35:38.87,0:35:45.60,Song,,0,0,0,,Than anyone else in your pupils
Dialogue: 10,0:35:45.60,0:35:57.47,Song,,0,0,0,,I'm putting on a brave front again
Dialogue: 10,0:35:57.47,0:36:03.24,Song,,0,0,0,,Your kindness is not enough
Dialogue: 10,0:35:59.05,0:36:01.10,Song,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H500580&\i1\an1\fs20}Please understand
Dialogue: 10,0:36:02.51,0:36:04.35,Song,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H500580&\i1\an1\fs20}Please watch my hand {no clue}
Dialogue: 10,0:36:04.35,0:36:09.86,Song,,0,0,0,,Which of us is going to say it?
Dialogue: 10,0:36:05.93,0:36:08.46,Song,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H500580&\i1\an1\fs20}Please take my heart {no clue}
Dialogue: 10,0:36:09.86,0:36:16.24,Song,,0,0,0,,But for now, we just fight all the time
Dialogue: 10,0:36:16.24,0:36:22.62,Song,,0,0,0,,I understand, I'll turn my back on you
Dialogue: 10,0:36:22.62,0:36:29.96,Song,,0,0,0,,I’m running alone down a slope under the setting sun
Dialogue: 10,0:36:29.96,0:36:36.18,Song,,0,0,0,,Please chase after me
Dialogue: 10,0:36:36.18,0:36:44.16,Song,,0,0,0,,Don't let this love go astray
